Bernardo Amaral

Hello! I'm a Portuguese MSc graduated student of Electrical and Computer Science at Instituto Superior Técnico Lisboa.

I finished my MSc Thesis on an Air Quality Monitoring and Interpolation System for IoT Applications in December 2020 with a final grade of 19.

My interests lie within the software development and data science fields.

I like to develop useful and fun ideas.
